metadata.title: Missing Links Vol 1 - 3
description: UK two CD set containing a trio of rarities albums from the former Genesis guitarist. Volume One, Finger Painting, is a collection of television and library music recorded between 1079 and 1989. Volume Two, Sky Road, is a set of archive, commissioned and previously unreleased material. Volume Three, Time & Tide, is a collection of television and library music recorded 1992 and 1997.
